OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly cloudy day with the
OL,6,Fchance of a light shower. A few bright
OL,7,For sunny spells may break through this
OL,8,Fafternoon. Fresh southeasterly winds
OL,9,Fat first across Shetland soon easing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry this evening. Thickening
OL,12,Fcloud will bring a few outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain during the early hours, this
OL,14,Fturning persistent across Orkney
OL,15,Flater. Freshening southeasterly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FRain spreading east during
OL,18,Fthe morning, clearing Orkney by late
OL,19,Fmorning and Shetland mid-afternoon.
OL,20,FBrighter weather following on behind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
